I meet a test case whose input is None and expected  is "a".

How is this possible?![0_1480802425220_Screen Shot 2016-12-03 at 4.58.28 PM.png](/uploads/files/1480802425962-screen-shot-2016-12-03-at-4.58.28-pm.png) 

@administrators

Java method semantics needs to be changed to make O(1) for space possible from:

public String reverseWords(String s)

to

public char[] reverseWords(char[] s) or public void reverseWords(char[] s)

Strings in java are immutable so it's technicaly not possible to solve with no extra space.
